---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Privacy Policy | The Life Insider"
  description="How The Life Insider collects, uses, and protects information when you visit our site."
>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container-narrow prose">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="updated">Last updated: July 2026</p>

      <p>
        This Privacy Policy explains how TheLifeInsider.com ("we", "us", "the
        site") collects, uses, and shares information when you visit or
        interact with our website.
      </p>

      <h2>Information we collect</h2>
      <h3>Information collected automatically</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Usage and analytics data.</strong> We use analytics services
          (including Google Analytics 4) to understand how visitors use the
          site — pages viewed, time on page, approximate location
          (city/region level), device and browser type, and how you arrived at
          the site. This data is aggregated and does not directly identify
          you.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Cookies and similar technologies.</strong> We and our
          service providers use cookies to operate the site, measure
          performance, attribute referrals to retail partners, and measure
          advertising effectiveness (including Google Ads conversion
          tracking). You can control cookies through your browser settings;
          disabling them may affect site functionality.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Affiliate click data.</strong> When you click an outbound
          retailer link, we and our retail partners may record that a click
          occurred (with a non-identifying reference ID) so that purchases can
          be attributed correctly.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Information you provide</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Contact information.</strong> If you email us or submit a
          contact form, we collect your name, email address, and message
          content to respond to you.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Email subscription.</strong> If you subscribe to our
          newsletter or deal alerts, we collect your email address. You can
          unsubscribe at any time via the link in every email.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How we use information</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>To operate, maintain, and improve the site and its content;</li>
        <li>To measure which content is useful and how visitors find us;</li>
        <li>To attribute purchases to our affiliate partnerships;</li>
        <li>To send emails you've requested (newsletters, deal alerts);</li>
        <li>To respond to your inquiries;</li>
        <li>To comply with legal obligations.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Sharing of information</h2>
      <p>We do not sell your personal information. We share data only with:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Service providers</strong> that help us run the site
          (hosting and content delivery, analytics, email delivery), bound by
          their own privacy obligations;
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Advertising and affiliate platforms</strong> (such as Google
          and retail affiliate networks) for conversion measurement and
          referral attribution;
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Authorities</strong> where required by law.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Third-party sites</h2>
      <p>
        Our site links to third-party retailers and brands. Once you leave our
        site, the destination site's privacy policy applies. We encourage you
        to review it before making a purchase.
      </p>

      <h2>Data retention</h2>
      <p>
        We retain analytics data for the standard retention period of our
        analytics providers, contact correspondence for as long as needed to
        resolve your inquiry, and email subscriptions until you unsubscribe.
      </p>

      <h2>Your rights</h2>
      <p>
        Depending on your location, you may have rights to access, correct,
        delete, or restrict the use of your personal information (including
        under the GDPR, the CCPA/CPRA, and the Australian Privacy Act). To
        exercise any of these rights, <a href="/contact/">contact us</a> and
        we will respond within a reasonable timeframe.
      </p>

      <h2>Children's privacy</h2>
      <p>
        Our site is not directed at children under 16, and we do not knowingly
        collect personal information from them.
      </p>

      <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this policy from time to time. Material changes will be
        reflected by the "Last updated" date at the top of this page.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Privacy questions or requests: <a href="/contact/">contact us here</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
